data.description:
Situated on a sprawling 3-acre parcel of open land, this newer-built ranch-style home offers a harmonious blend of modern comfort and expansive outdoor space, presenting a serene retreat for discerning homeowners. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, including a spacious primary suite, this residence provides a peaceful and inviting sanctuary for tranquil relaxation. Daylight basement ready for another bathroom and more bedrooms!

The property's standout feature is the expansive pole barn, providing ample space for storage, workshop areas, or hobbyist pursuits, further enhancing the possibilities for enjoying the outdoors and pursuing diverse interests.
